The STATE of Ohio, Appellee,
v.
WALKER, Appellant. No. 2018-0081 Supreme Court of Ohio. Submitted June 26, 2018
Decided December 13, 2018. Christopher R. Tunnell, Ashland County Prosecuting Attorney, and Victor R. Perez, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant. Gary D. Walker, pro se. O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

{¶ 1} This cause is dismissed as having been improvidently accepted.
